Laxman sir told me.. “Mimi, i wanna see your face and believe that you are pregnant “ 
Being blessed with a good metabolism and normally eating burgers and pizzas in life, gaining 15kgs was a challenge.. I never thought i could do it, and there was a point when I didn’t wanna see food.. but when i saw how it translated on screen, it was all worth it! 
 
Mimi Exclusive world premiere 30th July on @officialjiocinema & @netflix_in.

node.text:
In this pandemic many kids have lost one or both their parents. Many families have lost their only earning members. Many kids face horrors like sexual abuse and child labour. No child should have to go through a time in their life without basic human rights.

Lets make our 40 Million hearts beat together and do some good! Lets use the strength of this platform to put smiles on some faces.

I have joined hands with @ngoprotsahan PROTSAHAN to help them generate money that can be used in providing High protein Ration kits to children, pregnant and lactating mothers, in providing children with educational kits, trauma counselling and all that is needed to help secure their childhood!

If each one of us donates even 1 Rupee (ofcourse you can donate more if it comes from your heart and doesn’t hurt your pocket), we can possibly generate 40M rupees!!(Thats HUGE)
I urge you all to pls donate using the link in my BIO. I will put the same on my Story with a Swipe Up and will also put it in my highlights! 

Lets do this!! 
#WeAreInThisTogether ❤️
#40MillionStrong
#KritiSanonxProtsahan
